∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Fintype F] [inst_1 : Field F] {b c : F},
  Odd (Fintype.card F) →
    Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
    Nat.card {d : F // Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c + Polynomial.C d)} = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2

∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Fintype F] [inst_1 : Field F] {b c : F},
  Odd (Fintype.card F) →
  Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
  ∃ (s : Finset F), s.card = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2 ∧
    ∀ d ∈ s, Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C (c + d))

∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Fintype F] [inst_1 : Field F] {b c : F},
  Odd (Fintype.card F) →
    Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
    Fintype.card {d : F // Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C (c + d))} = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2

∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Fintype F] [inst_1 : Field F] {b c : F},
  Odd (Fintype.card F) →
  Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
  (∃ m : ℕ, m = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2 ∧
    ∃ S : Finset F, S.card = m ∧
      ∀ d : F, d ∈ S ↔
        Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C (c + d)))

∀ {F : Type u} [inst : Field F] [inst_1 : Fintype F] {b c : F},
  Fintype.card F % 2 = 1 →
  Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
  Fintype.card {d // Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C (c + d))} = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2

∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Fintype F] [inst_1 : Field F] {b c : F},
  Odd (Fintype.card F) →
    Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
      (∃ (d : Finset F), d.card = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2 ∧ ∀ x ∈ d, Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c + Polynomial.C x))

∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Fintype F] [inst_1 : Field F] (n : ℕ) (b c : F),
  Odd n → (∀ x, x^2 + b*x + c ≠ 0) →
  Nat.card {d // ∀ x, x^2 + b*x + c + d ≠ 0} = (n - 1) / 2

∀ {F : Type u} [inst : Fintype F] [inst_1 : Field F] {b c : F},
  Odd (Fintype.card F) →
    Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
    Finset.card {d ∈ Finset.univ | Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c + Polynomial.C d)} = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2

∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Fintype F] [inst_1 : Field F] {b c : F},
  Odd (Fintype.card F) → Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
  Fintype.card {d : F // Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C (c + d))} = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2

∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Fintype F] [inst_1 : Field F] {b c : F},
  Odd (Fintype.card F) →
    Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
      (Fintype.card {d : F // Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C (c + d))}) = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2
